Kohana Notice
=============

Release: 0.4.1


Description
-----------

Notice is simple and easy to use class for storing and displaying
notification messages to a user for Kohana 3.x.

Installation instructions
-------------------------

Requirements:

 - PHP 5.3.3 or newer
 - Kohana 3.3 or newer

Installing:

 - Install Notice by downloading the source or by using Composer
 - Enable module in the *bootstrap*

More information:

 - Using Kohana modules [http://kohanaframework.org/3.3/guide/kohana/modules]
 - Using Composer [http://www.getcomposer.org/]


Documentation
-------------

Documentation is available under the 'guide/notice' directory. If you
still need help, open a support ticket on the Github
[http://github.com/loonies/kohana-notice/issues].


Contributing
------------

Open an issue or send a pull request on the Github
[http://github.com/loonies/kohana-notice].

Please use Kohana conventions and coding style.


